notes: The match was reduced to 44 overs per side due to a late start as the WI cricket kit wrongly went to Madras.
West Indies were fined 1 over for a slow over rate

milestones.description: Azharuddin has broken the record for most catches (73) in ODIs for IND, going past Kapil Dev's 71
Navjot Sidhu has scored 5 hundreds in ODIs, the most for IND breaking Ravi Shastri's record
